Package schedule.manager.service.provided.csv

Class ScheduleManagerCSV

java.lang.Object
schedule.manager.service.provided.csv.ScheduleManagerCSV
All Implemented Interfaces:
ScheduleExporter, ScheduleImporter, ScheduleManagerService
public class ScheduleManagerCSV extends Object implements ScheduleManagerService
The ScheduleManagerCSV class is responsible for loading and exporting lecture data from/to CSV files. It implements the ScheduleManagerService interface.
